| | | | ☐ |

### 6.3 Polish Checklist

- [ ] No dramatic language without dramatic evidence
- [ ] Statistics exact
- [ ] Metaphors consistent
- [ ] All citations `[ShortName, location]` format
- [ ] No fabricated references
- [ ] Conflicts acknowledged
- [ ] Narrative integrated (no doc-by-doc structure)

### 6.4 Length Check

| Target | Actual | Status |
|--------|--------|--------|
| | | OK / Over / Under |

---

## Pass 7: Output

Produce the final deliverable based on Pass 1.4 assessment:
- **Sufficient/Marginal** → Executive Summary + Process Notes
- **Insufficient** → Research Gap Assessment + Process Notes

